School: Transmutation
Components: V,S
Range: Touch
Target: You or creature touched
Duration: ((Caster Level/2) - 10) turns; with a minimum of 5 turns, and with a maximum of 10 turns.
Saving Throw: None (harmless)
Spell Resistance: No (harmless)

Battles require prowess and accuracy of motion, in addition to the strategy and numbers and morale. With the +20 to attack bonus granted by this spell, the subjects swing of the sword will be more precise, and the aim with their bow will be more true.